      Classes in hr.fer.zemris.java.hw10.jnotepadpp.localize that implement ILocalizationProvider 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractLocalizationProvider
      Implements ILocalizationProvider interface and adds it the ability to register, de-register and inform (fire() method) listeners.
      class  FormLocalizationProvider
      Class derived from LocalizationProviderBridge; in its constructor it registers itself as a WindowListener to its JFrame; when frame is opened, it calls connect and when frame is closed, it calls disconnect.
      class  LocalizationProvider
      Singleton, main role of this class is to get instance of localization provider.
      class  LocalizationProviderBridge
      Decorator for ILocalizationProvider.
